reviewText: The are a lot of good things in this compilation, along with one or two really excellent pieces. The on camera extras with Carol and some of the other cast members, were slightly uncomfortable to watch, and could have been left off the disc.  Well worth it for 'Went with the Wind', 'As the Stomach Turns' and Tim Conway's skit as a dentist, which was included in the extras.
